  <brief_title>StaphVAX in Cardiovascular Surgery Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double-Blinded Study to Evaluate Safety and Immunogenicity of StaphVAX速, a Bivalent Staphylococcus Aureus Glycoconjugate Vaccine, in Adult Patients Undergoing Cardiovascular Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
