  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Candidate for cardiovascular surgery

          -  Expected to comply with protocol

          -  Negative pregnancy test where appropriate

          -  Written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known S. aureus infection in past 3 months

          -  Known infection in the past 2 weeks

          -  Known HIV infection

          -  Pregnancy or breast-feeding

          -  Immunomodulatory drugs

          -  Malignancy or treatment for malignancy within the past six months, other than basal
             cell, localized squamous cell carcinoma of the skin, carcinoma in situ of the cervix,
             or early stage prostate cancer

          -  investigational drugs, vaccines or products in the past 30 days

          -  Hypersensitivity to components of StaphVAX
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
